						<p>Busy families, working professionals, and anyone who wants to maintain a consistently clean home</p>
						<h3>Frequency Options:</h3>
						<p>Weekly, Bi-weekly, or Monthly</p>
						<h3>Pricing Based On:</h3>
						<p>Square footage of your home</p>
