					<div class="service-description">
						<h3>What's Included:</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Everything in Regular Cleaning, plus:</li>
							<li>Baseboard and trim detailed cleaning</li>
							<li>Inside appliances (add-ons available)</li>
							<li>Cabinet exterior cleaning</li>
							<li>Window sills and tracks</li>
							<li>Light fixtures and ceiling fan cleaning</li>
							<li>Door frames and detailed woodwork</li>
							<li>Behind and under furniture</li>
							<li>Blind dusting and wiping</li>
							<li>More thorough attention to every surface</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="service-details-box">
						<h3>Perfect For:</h3>
						<p>Spring cleaning, preparing for guests, seasonal refresh, or when your home needs extra attention</p>
						<h3>Time Required:</h3>
						<p>3-6 hours depending on home size</p>
						<h3>Recommended:</h3>
						<p>Quarterly or as needed</p>
