					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div id="move" class="service-detail">
				<div class="service-header">
					<div>
						<h2>Move In/Move Out Cleaning</h2>
						<p class="service-intro">Ensure a fresh start in your new home or leave your old one spotless.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="pricing-badge">
						<span class="price-label">Starting at</span>
						<span class="price-amount">$378</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="service-content">
					<div class="service-description">
						<h3>What's Included:</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Complete deep cleaning of entire property</li>
							<li>All cabinets and drawers (inside and out)</li>
							<li>All appliances thoroughly cleaned</li>
							<li>Walls spot cleaned and wiped down</li>
							<li>Closets vacuumed and wiped</li>
							<li>Window cleaning (interior)</li>
							<li>Bathroom deep clean and sanitization</li>
							<li>Floor cleaning (vacuum, mop, or both)</li>
							<li>Baseboards and trim cleaning</li>
							<li>Light fixtures and fans</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="service-details-box">
						<h3>Perfect For:</h3>
						<p>Tenants, landlords, home buyers, home sellers, and real estate agents</p>
						<h3>Satisfaction Guarantee:</h3>
						<p>We'll make it right if you're not 100% satisfied</p>
						<h3>Popular With:</h3>
						<p>Property managers and real estate professionals</p>
						<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book Now</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div id="office" class="service-detail">
				<div class="service-header">
					<div>
						<h2>Office Cleaning</h2>
						<p class="service-intro">Professional office cleaning customized for your business needs.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="pricing-badge custom">
						<span class="price-label">Custom</span>
						<span class="price-amount">Quote</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="service-content">
					<div class="service-description">
						<h3>Services Available:</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Regular office maintenance cleaning</li>
							<li>Restroom sanitization</li>
							<li>Break room and kitchen cleaning</li>
							<li>Vacuuming and floor care</li>
							<li>Trash removal and recycling</li>
							<li>Surface disinfection</li>
							<li>Window cleaning</li>
							<li>Flexible scheduling (after hours available)</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="service-details-box">
						<h3>Perfect For:</h3>
						<p>Small businesses, professional offices, medical offices, and retail spaces</p>
						<h3>Custom Scheduling:</h3>
						<p>Daily, weekly, bi-weekly, or monthly service</p>
						<h3>Get a Quote:</h3>
						<p>Call (865) 507-1405 for custom pricing based on your office size and needs</p>
						<a href="tel:865-507-1405" class="btn btn-primary">Call for Quote</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div id="airbnb" class="service-detail">
				<div class="service-header">
					<div>
						<h2>Airbnb/Vacation Rental Cleaning</h2>
						<p class="service-intro">Fast turnaround cleaning between guests. Keep your ratings high!</p>
					</div>
					<div class="pricing-badge custom">
						<span class="price-label">Custom</span>
						<span class="price-amount">Quote</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="service-content">
					<div class="service-description">
						<h3>Turnover Service Includes:</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Complete cleaning between guests</li>
							<li>Linen service (strip, wash, remake beds)</li>
							<li>Bathroom deep clean and restocking</li>
							<li>Kitchen cleaning and restocking</li>
							<li>Trash removal</li>
							<li>Floor cleaning throughout</li>
							<li>Quality check before guest arrival</li>
							<li>Same-day turnaround available</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="service-details-box">
						<h3>Perfect For:</h3>
						<p>Airbnb hosts, VRBO owners, vacation rental property managers</p>
						<h3>Turnaround Time:</h3>
						<p>Same-day or next-day service available</p>
						<h3>Get a Quote:</h3>
						<p>Call (865) 507-1405 for pricing based on property size and frequency</p>
						<a href="tel:865-507-1405" class="btn btn-primary">Call for Quote</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="service-detail">
				<h2>Add-On Services</h2>
				<p class="service-intro">Enhance any cleaning with these popular add-ons:</p>
				<div class="addons-grid">
					<div class="addon-card">
						<div class="addon-price">$50</div>
						<h3>Pet Hair Removal</h3>
						<p>Extra attention to pet hair and dander throughout your home</p>
					</div>
					<div class="addon-card">
						<div class="addon-price">$75</div>
						<h3>Extra 1000 Sq Ft</h3>
						<p>For larger homes, add per additional 1000 square feet</p>
					</div>
					<div class="addon-card">
						<div class="addon-price">$137</div>
						<h3>Carpet Cleaning</h3>
						<p>Professional carpet deep cleaning service</p>
					</div>
					<div class="addon-card">
						<div class="addon-price">$12/window</div>
						<h3>Interior Windows</h3>
						<p>Crystal-clear window cleaning</p>
					</div>
					<div class="addon-card">
						<div class="addon-price">$75</div>
						<h3>Inside Refrigerator</h3>
						<p>Deep clean and sanitize refrigerator interior</p>
					</div>
					<div class="addon-card">
						<div class="addon-price">$40</div>
						<h3>Inside Cabinets</h3>
						<p>Cabinet interior cleaning and organizing</p>
					</div>
					<div class="addon-card">
						<div class="addon-price">$50</div>
						<h3>Heavy Duty Clean</h3>
						<p>Extra attention for heavily soiled areas</p>
					</div>
					<div class="addon-card">
						<div class="addon-price">$20</div>
						<h3>Wet Wipe Blinds</h3>
