						<h3>Dishes</h3>
						<p>Wash and put away dishes</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="pricing-note">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Transparent Pricing You Can Trust</h2>
			<p>Unlike our competitors who hide pricing, we believe in transparency. All prices are based on your home's square footage. Final quotes provided after a brief consultation.</p>
			<div class="pricing-features">
				<div class="pricing-feature">
					<strong>✓ No Hidden Fees</strong>
					<p>What you see is what you pay</p>
				</div>
				<div class="pricing-feature">
					<strong>✓ Instant Online Quotes</strong>
					<p>Get pricing in seconds</p>
				</div>
				<div class="pricing-feature">
					<strong>✓ Price Match Guarantee</strong>
					<p>We'll match any competitor's written quote</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-large btn-primary">Get Your Free Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-header {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		color: white;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.page-header p {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
	}

	.services-section {
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
	}

	.service-detail {
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
		padding-bottom: 4rem;
		border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
	}

	.service-detail:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}

	.service-header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.service-detail h2 {
		color: var(--primary);
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.service-intro {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--text-light);
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.pricing-badge {
		background: var(--primary);
		color: white;
		padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		text-align: center;
		min-width: 140px;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.pricing-badge.custom {
		background: var(--secondary);
	}

	.price-label {
		display: block;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		opacity: 0.9;
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}

	.price-amount {
		display: block;
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.service-content {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.service-description h3 {
		color: var(--text);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.service-description ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.service-description li {
		padding: 0.5rem 0;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
		position: relative;
		color: var(--text-light);
	}

	.service-description li::before {
		content: "✓";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--secondary);
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	.service-details-box {
		background: var(--bg-light);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		height: fit-content;
	}

	.service-details-box h3 {
		color: var(--text);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.service-details-box h3:first-child {
		margin-top: 0;
	}

	.service-details-box p {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.service-details-box .btn {
		width: 100%;
		text-align: center;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.addons-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.addon-card {
		background: white;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		border: 2px solid var(--border);
		transition: all 0.3s;
	}

	.addon-card:hover {
		border-color: var(--primary);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
	}

	.addon-price {
		background: var(--secondary);
		color: white;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 0.25rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		display: inline-block;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.addon-card h3 {
		color: var(--text);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.addon-card p {
		color: var(--text-light);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.pricing-note {
		background: var(--bg-light);
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.pricing-note h2 {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.pricing-note > .container > p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.pricing-features {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin: 3rem auto;
		max-width: 900px;
	}

	.pricing-feature {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.pricing-feature strong {
		display: block;
		color: var(--secondary);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.pricing-feature p {
		color: var(--text-light);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
		transition: all 0.3s;
	}

	.btn-large {
		padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.service-header {
			flex-direction: column;
		}

		.pricing-badge {
			width: 100%;
		}

		.service-content {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.page-header h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.addons-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.pricing-features {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
